Systematic notes on Neotropical Checkered Beetles of the genus Enoclerus Gahan (Coleoptera: Cleridae)One new species of the genus Enoclerus Gahan, E. alicei sp. n., is described from Mexico. Enoclerus laticinctus (White), resurrected specific epithet, is shown to be a senior rather than junior homonym of E. latecinctus (LeConte). Clerus lateluteus Pic is placed as a synonym of E. laticinctus (White). E. laticinctus is recorded for the first time from Colombia.